<node ID="92AEA1C5-75EB-404B-85BC-53C0F89DA152" TEXT="&#27880;&#20837; API" COLOR="#36342E" POSITION="right" STYLE="fork"><edge COLOR="#48B04B" WIDTH="5" /><font NAME="PingFangSC-Light" SIZE="21" /><richcontent TYPE="NOTE"><html><head></head>
<body><p><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>基于</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '> Webview </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>提供的能力，我们可以向</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '> Window </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>上注入对象或方法。</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>JS </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>通过这个对象或方法进行调用时，执行对应的逻辑操作，可以直接调用</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '> Native </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>的方法。使用该方式时，</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>JS </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>需要等到</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '> Native </span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>执行完对应的逻辑后才能进行回调里面的操作。</span></p><p></p><p style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>作者：政采云前端团队</p><p><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>链接：</span><span style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "Helvetica Neue"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "HelveticaNeue"; '>https://juejin.im/post/5e5248216fb9a07cb0314fc9</span></p><p style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>来源：掘金</p><p style='color: rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.000000); font: 15px "PingFang SC"; -cocoa-font-postscriptname: "PingFangSC-Regular"; '>著作权归作者所有。商业转载请联系作者获得授权，非商业转载请注明出处。</p></body>
</html>
</richcontent>
